{"word":"ἀμηχανία","slug":"ἀμηχανία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀμηχανία</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:ἀμήχανος'><el>ἀμήχανος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>want of means, helplessness, impotence</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>ὑπ' ἀμηχανίας</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of things, <i>hardship, trouble</i>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}